fm: int minEatingSpeed(vector<int> &piles, int H) {         int i = 1, j = pow(10, 9), mid = 1;         while (i < j) {             mid = i + (j - i) / 2;             if (CanEat(piles, H, mid))                 j = mid;             else                 i = mid + 1;         }         return j;     }

fm: bool stoneGame(vector<int> &piles) {         int size = piles.size();         vector<vector<int>> dp(size, vector<int>(size, 0));         for (int i = 0; i < size; ++i)             dp[i][i] = piles[i];         for (int i = 1; i < size; ++i) {             for (int j = i - 1; j >= 0; --j)                 dp[j][i] = max(piles[j] - dp[j + 1][i], piles[i] - dp[j][i - 1]);         }         return dp[0][size - 1];     }
